<html><body>
<h1 align="center">Changelog</h1>
<h1 align="center">07/08/2024 - 17/08/2024</h1>
<h2 align="left">Class issues</h2>
<p>Elementals summoned by shamans' totems no longer follow the shaman out of combat.</p>
<p>This has created a new issue causing elementals to attack units that they shouldn't, such as opposite faction players.<br /><br /></p>
<h2 align="left">Instance issues</h2>
<p align="center">Dungeons</p>
<p>Level 70 Elite Tauren Chieftain has returned from retirement! The band now performs in the Grim Guzzler in Blackrock Depths at 8PM server time every evening.<br /><br /></p>
<h2 align="left">Generic issues</h2>
<p>Several improvements have been made to various spells, including Ritual of Refreshment, Souls, and Summoning. Also includes improvements to meeting stone summoning.</p>
<p>Spells that trigger other spells that scale damage based on the level of the caster no longer get scaled twice.<br /><br /></p>
<h2 align="left">Open world issues</h2>
<p>The Dragonmaw racers now reset properly after they've finished a race.</p>
<p>L70ETC will now also perform every four hours in Shattrath's World's End Tavern. The band members in Silvermoon City will also now respond to emotes.</p>
<p>Shattrath Saul in the World's End Tavern now also properly walks around the city to herald incoming performances both from L70ETC and Perry Gatner.</p>
</body></html>
